    <title>Hexo-Theme-Lx</title>
    <url>/200318/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Tue Mar 24 2020 12:36:31 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间) --><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/blleng/lx/assets/5.jpeg" alt="Cover"></p><p><code>Lx</code> is a simple &amp; clear &amp; elegant hexo theme.<br>Current version: <code>V0.3.8</code></p><p>Languages: <a href="/190607/">中文</a>,English</p><p>Source on GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx</a></p><a id="more"></a><div class="note success"><p>Source on GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx</a></p><p>Telegram hexo-thme-lx：<a href="https://t.me/themelx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://t.me/themelx</a></p><p>Any problem,suggestion or bug report:<br><a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/issues</a></p></div><div class="note warning"><p>This site aims to provide a live demo for <code>lx</code> and won’t offer help.<br>Any problem,suggestion or bug report –&gt; <a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Issue</a></p></div><h2 id="Latest-release"><a href="#Latest-release" class="headerlink" title="Latest release"></a>Latest release</h2><h3 id="V0-3-8"><a href="#V0-3-8" class="headerlink" title="V0.3.8"></a>V0.3.8</h3><ul><li>Theme color on Chrome for Android</li><li>Home page improved</li><li>Bugs fixed</li></ul><h2 id="Usage"><a href="#Usage" class="headerlink" title="Usage"></a>Usage</h2><h3 id="Stable-version"><a href="#Stable-version" class="headerlink" title="Stable version:"></a>Stable version:</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/releases</a></p><p>Unzip the package and put the files under <code>themes</code>. Rename it as <code>lx</code>.</p><blockquote><p>Don’t use V0.3.3 and V0.3.5！</p></blockquote><h3 id="Latest-version"><a href="#Latest-version" class="headerlink" title="Latest version:"></a>Latest version:</h3><p>At the root dir of your site:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx themes/lx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>The latest verion may have bugs.</p></blockquote><h3 id="Edit-the-config-file"><a href="#Edit-the-config-file" class="headerlink" title="Edit the config file:"></a>Edit the config file:</h3><p>Edit the <code>_config.yml</code> file under root dir:</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">lx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Functions"><a href="#Functions" class="headerlink" title="Functions"></a>Functions</h2><p>More features in <code>README.md</code>:</p><a class="btn" href="https://github.com/blleng/hexo-theme-lx/blob/master/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right fa-fw"></i>hexo-theme-lx</a><h2 id="Done"><a href="#Done" class="headerlink" title="Done"></a>Done</h2><ul><li>Comment</li><li>Analytics<ul><li>Baidu Analytics</li><li>Goole Analytics</li><li>Mathjax</li></ul></li><li>Font Awesome</li><li>Some tags from NexT<ul><li>label</li><li>button</li><li>note</li><li>video</li><li>etc…</li></ul></li><li>Sidebar</li><li>Social links</li><li>Local Search</li><li>tags of post</li><li>category of post</li><li>Jsdelivr CDN</li></ul><h2 id="To-Do"><a href="#To-Do" class="headerlink" title="To Do"></a>To Do</h2><ul><li>PJAX</li><li>Fancybox</li></ul><h2 id="Test"><a href="#Test" class="headerlink" title="Test"></a>Test</h2><h3 id="Mathjax"><a href="#Mathjax" class="headerlink" title="Mathjax"></a>Mathjax</h3><p>万有引力常数为 \(G\) ,对于质量分别为 \(M\) 和 \(m\) ，球心距离为 \(r\) 的两个正球形天体，两者间相互作用力:<br>$$F=\frac{GMm}{r^2}$$</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">万有引力常数为\\(G\\),对于质量分别为\\(M\\)和\\(m\\)，球心距离为\\(r\\)的两个正球形天体，两者间相互作用力:</span><br><span class="line">$$F=\frac&#123;GMm&#125;&#123;r^2&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>化学方程式:</p><p>$$\ce{CH2=CH2 + Cl2 -&gt; CH2Cl-CH2Cl}$$</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$\ce&#123;CH2=CH2 + Cl2 -&gt; CH2Cl-CH2Cl&#125;$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Code-block"><a href="#Code-block" class="headerlink" title="Code block"></a>Code block</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> namespae <span class="built_in">std</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"hello world!"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Note-tag"><a href="#Note-tag" class="headerlink" title="Note tag"></a>Note tag</h3><div class="note default"><h4 id="note-default"><a href="#note-default" class="headerlink" title="note default"></a>note default</h4><p>default</p></div><div class="note info"><h4 id="note-info"><a href="#note-info" class="headerlink" title="note info"></a>note info</h4><p>info</p></div><div class="note primary"><h4 id="note-primary"><a href="#note-primary" class="headerlink" title="note primary"></a>note primary</h4><p>primary</p></div><div class="note success"><h4 id="note-success"><a href="#note-success" class="headerlink" title="note success"></a>note success</h4><p>success</p></div><div class="note warning"><h4 id="note-warning"><a href="#note-warning" class="headerlink" title="note warning"></a>note warning</h4><p>warning</p></div><div class="note danger"><h4 id="note-danger"><a href="#note-danger" class="headerlink" title="note danger"></a>note danger</h4><p>danger</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note default%&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### note default</span></span><br><span class="line">default</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Label-tag"><a href="#Label-tag" class="headerlink" title="Label tag"></a>Label tag</h3><span class="label default">复道</span><span class="label primary">行空</span>，<span class="label default">不霁</span><span class="label success">何虹</span>。 <span class="label info">长桥</span><span class="label danger">卧波</span>，<span class="label warning">未云</span><mark>何龙</mark>。<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%label @复道%&#125;&#123;%label primary@行空%&#125;，&#123;%label default@不霁%&#125;&#123;%label success@何虹%&#125;。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;%label info@长桥%&#125;&#123;%label danger@卧波%&#125;，&#123;%label warning@未云%&#125;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>何龙<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">mark</span>&gt;</span></span>。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Button-tag"><a href="#Button-tag" class="headerlink" title="Button tag"></a>Button tag</h3><p>Button</p><a class="btn" href="#url" title="title">test_tile</a><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%btn #url,test_tile,,title%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Icon</p><a class="btn" href="#url"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>test_tile</a><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%btn #url,test_tile,hand-o-right%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Fix-width</p><a class="btn" href="#url"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right fa-fw"></i>test_tile</a><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%btn #url,test_tile,hand-o-right fa-fw %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Center-quote-tag"><a href="#Center-quote-tag" class="headerlink" title="Center-quote tag"></a>Center-quote tag</h3><blockquote class="blockquote-center"><p>人类的悲欢并不相通，我只觉得他们吵闹。<br><strong>——鲁迅</strong></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%cq%&#125; something &#123;%endcq%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Video-tag"><a href="#Video-tag" class="headerlink" title="Video tag"></a>Video tag</h3><video src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/blleng/lx/assets/zhonghang.mp4" preload="metadata" controls playsinline poster="">Sorry, your browser does not support the video tag.</video><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% video url %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
